data.description: Extraordinary opportunity to own this 2-level Lake view home with year-round lake views in Beaver Shores! There are 2 boat launches located in the neighborhood, with one approx. 500 feet away! Two beds, 1 1/2 bath home with office/study (could be converted to a 3rd bedroom & 1/2 bath could be converted to another full bath), 2 large living areas, rock bar, breakfast area, 2 levels of covered porches, and large picture windows overlooking gorgeous year-round lake views! Potential to be a 3 bed, 2 full bath home! Just minutes from downtown Rogers, this Beaver Lake view home is a rare find! Two wood burning fireplaces, for relaxing after a long day! Many updates, including a full gourmet kitchen with island bar & granite countertops, fresh paint inside/out, wood laminate flooring downstairs, etc! A dream come true! Perfect for a personal or vacation home! Walk or ride 4-wheelers to lake.
